  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Morbidity at 60 days postoperatively of the 2 techniques</measure>
    <time_frame>60-90 days</time_frame>
    <description>Morbidity at 60 days postoperatively of the 2 techniques, the morbidity being defined as &quot; the sum of adverse events that occurred during or after the procedure for a period of 2 months&quot;.Primary outcome measure is &quot;the percentage of patients with complication, whatever the number of complications per patient and the grade of complication according to the Clavien-Dindo classification&quot;.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
